StructureDefinitionKind

Defines the type of structure that a definition is describing.

This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/structure-definition-kind defines the following codes:

Code Display Definition
datatype Data Type A data type - either a primitive or complex structure that defines a set of data elements. These can be used throughout Resource and extension definitions.
resource Resource A resource defined by the FHIR specification.
logical Logical Model A logical model - a conceptual package of data that will be mapped to resources for implementation.
